trans-unit.source: Describes the current state of a <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance.
The <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance is being used as storage for the <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogStore" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> 인스턴스가 <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogStore" />의 저장소로 사용되고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance is marked for deletion but still contains some active data.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> 인스턴스가 삭제되도록 표시되어 있지만 일부 활성 데이터를 포함하고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance has been allocated to the <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogStore" /> but does not contain any active data.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> 인스턴스가 <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogStore" />에 할당되었지만 활성 데이터를 포함하고 있지 않습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance has not yet been allocated to the <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogStore" />.
The <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance does not contain any active data, but contains data that has not yet been archived.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> 인스턴스가 활성 데이터를 포함하지 않지만 보관되지 않은 데이터를 포함하고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance is marked for deletion but still contains data that has not been archived.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> 인스턴스가 삭제되도록 표시되어 있지만 보관되지 않은 데이터를 포함하고 있습니다.

trans-unit.source: The status of the <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> instance is unknown.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.IO.Log.LogExtent" /> 인스턴스의 상태를 알 수 없습니다.
